   "source": "# Fake News Detection - End-to-End NLP Project\n\nA small classifier that reads a news headline and decides if it's fake (0) or real (1). The whole pipeline lives in this single notebook: load the data, clean it, vectorise it, train a few models, evaluate the best one, and generate predictions for the unlabelled test set.\n\n```\nraw csv  ->  clean  ->  preprocess  ->  vectorise  ->  train  ->  evaluate  ->  predict\n```"
  },
